name: Colonel Mustard Tee
description: This t-shirt lists all of our shows from 2007 to 2011 and features a quotation from our hero Albert Watkins on the front.

name: X Files: The Musical: The DVD (pre-order)
description:
This DVD of the show has lots of camera angles and includes behind-the-scenes footage, writer commentaries, and concept art. The complete XFTM experience! The DVD should be completed during September 2011, and we expect to ship out the first batch of DVD orders in October.

Just so you know, the footage of the musical will eventually be posted to Youtube. So if you just want to see what the show was all about, you'll be able to see it on the "cmustardtheatre" channel. However, the behind-the-scenes DVD extras won't be available online.

name: Jurassic Park The Musical!: The DVD
description: 65 million fans can't be wrong. JPTM is the must have DVD for 2009. Or 2011. Pretty much whatever year it is, you've gotta give this to every paleontologist in your family.

name: JPTM/XFTM DVD combo pack
description:
Best deal around. Get both of our profesh-ish-ionally produced DVDs at a low, low price. For the avid Mustard lover.

Jurassic Park The Musical! DVDs already exist, but our videographer is currently editing X Files: The Musical. You can expect the combo pack to be shipped during October 2011, after we put the XFTM footage together.

name: XFTM tee
description: The shirt that started it all. Great design, plus it's comfy and wearing it grants you access to gas stations. As long as you also wear shoes. (Shoes not included.) NOTE: The shirt is actually a nice charcoal gray - it's not as black as it appears in the image to the left.
